methods.make:
Create a field copier from a GenericRecord to the given chunk and data type

:param fieldName: (java.lang.String) - the name of the field in the generic record
:param chunkType: (io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.ChunkType) - the type of chunk in the publisher
:param dataType: (java.lang.Class<?>) - the dataType in the output definition
:return: (io.deephaven.kafka.ingest.GenericRecordFieldCopier) a GenericRecordField copier for the given field and destination type

text: A field copier that handles generic records.
